			</p>
			<p>
				When you subscribe to UCanBe, we collect personal information such as your name, e-mail address, shipping address and credit card information. We use this information to process and fulfill your order and to notify you of your order status. All archived credit card information is maintained in a secure and safe environment as described in this privacy policy.
			</p>
			<p>
				UCanBe automatically receives and records information on our server logs from your browser, including your IP address, cookies, and the pages you request.
			</p>
			<p>
				UCanBe uses information for the following general purposes: products and services provisioning, billing, identification and authentication, services improvement, contact, research, and anonymous reporting. IP addresses are automatically reported by your browser each time you view a web page.
